  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Thread doraji onto skewers, leaving a little space between each piece.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together Australian olive oil, ginger, and garlic. Brush the mixture onto the doraji skewers.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Grill the skewers for 2-3 minutes per side, or until slightly charred.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together crunchy peanut butter, crisp cabbage, and lime juice. Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Serve the grilled doraji skewers with Australian slaw on the side.",
    "Garnish with additional ginger slices, if desired."
